<section id="fb1">
	<p align="left">1.<font color="#0000ff">&#32;<b>shopping</b>: credit card, to spend money, to try things on, a price, to buy</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb2">
	<p align="left">2. <font color="#0000ff"><b>playing board games</b>: to cheat, to lose, to win, to beat, backgammon, chess, draughts</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb3">
	<p align="left">3. <font color="#0000ff"><b>listening to music</b>: CDs, tapes, a Walkman, headphones, pop, jazz</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb4">
	<p align="left">4. <font color="#0000ff"><b>going to the cinema</b>: a science fiction film, the big screen, special effects, horror films</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb5">
	<p align="left">5. <font color="#0000ff"><b>eating out</b>: cuisine, a restaurant, a starter, a main course, desserts, a three-course meal</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb6">
	<p align="left">6. <font color="#0000ff"><b>cooking</b>: ingredients, recipes, dinner parties, the washing-up</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb7">
	<p align="left">7. <font color="#0000ff"><b>watching television</b>: the box, soap operas, sitcoms, game shows, chat shows, commercials</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb8">
	<p align="left">8. <font color="#0000ff"><b>reading</b>: a paperback, romantic fiction, a detective story</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb9">
	<p align="left">9. <font color="#0000ff"><b>photography</b>: a darkroom, to develop, films, to print, pictures, black and white, colour</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb10">
	<p align="left">10. <font color="#0000ff"><b>keep-fit</b>: health and fitness, a gym, weight training, stretching, a step machine, a treadmill, aerobics classes</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb11">
	<p align="left">11. <font color="#0000ff"><b>going to amusement parks</b>: a ride, the Big Dipper, attractions, a ghost train, a hall of mirrors</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb12">
	<p align="left">12. <font color="#0000ff"><b>dancing</b>: a bouncer, a club, a DJ, disco music</font></p>
